## Project Overview

FastAPI REST API for user authentication and profile management.
Supports OAuth2 (Google, GitHub), JWT sessions, and profile CRUD operations.

## Quick Start

```bash
uv sync                              # Install dependencies
docker compose up -d                 # Start PostgreSQL + Redis
uv run alembic upgrade head          # Apply migrations
uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload # Start dev server (localhost:8000)
uv run pytest                        # Run test suite
```

## Key Files

- `src/app/main.py` - FastAPI application entry point
- `src/app/core/config.py` - Settings (Pydantic BaseSettings)
- `src/app/core/security.py` - JWT and OAuth2 utilities
- `src/app/api/deps.py` - Dependency injection (db, auth)
- `tests/conftest.py` - pytest fixtures and test database setup

